race.description: Magic Millions March Yearling Sale Open Handicap
race.comment: SUPER DUCK (9) resumed in the Listed 1100m Gold Coast Goldmarket last start and was not disgraced, beaten just over three lengths. Carries 2kgs less in a weaker race and the second-up form is much better. Distance specialist who just needs a pinch of luck from an awkward gate to be right in the finish. The speedster HELL (3) led until nailed by HATCHET near the line when attempting back-to-back wins over this trip at the Sunshine Coast a fortnight ago. The winner of five from nine at 1200m, including a couple here. Will look the winner at some stage. HATCHET (2) beat some of today's key rivals two weeks ago. Evergreen sprinter who can never be ruled out. WEIGALL TIGER (4) is a strong first-up performer who is in the mix off a 20-week break.
